<div class="item" id="author-instruction">
    <ol class='decimal'>
        <p class="header" >INSTRUCTIONS FOR ONLINE SUBMISSION OF MANUSCRIPTS</p>
        <div class="item" >
            <li>
                Firstly, you need to log into the system. If you have a valid user name 
                (i.e. you have submitted or reviewed a manuscript on this system before), 
                use your User Name and Password to log on.
            </li>
        </div>
        <div class="item" >
            <li>Prepare your manuscript as a doc, pdf or tex file. 
            </li>
        </div>
        <div class="item" >
            <li>For online submission, please upload the low-resolution versions of the figures as separate files.</li>
        </div>

        <div class="item" >
            <li>Prepare any other files that should be submitted for review such as supplementary material. 
            The permitted formats for these files are the same as for manuscripts. Other file types such as Microsoft Excel 
            and Powerpoint presentations are acceptable.
            </li>
        </div>
        <div class="item" >
            <li>When naming your files, please use normal characters and avoid special characters and spaces.</li>
        </div> 
    </ol>
</div>